The Granadiers loyal health A song.
1 sheet ([1] p.).
Printed for J. Dean, in Cranborn-Street, in Leicester-Fields near Newport-House, [London] : 1683.
Place of publication from Wing. Verse - "Old England's glory now begins,". Includes 1 staff of music. Identified both as Wing G1485 (reel 1551) and Wing G1934A (reel 1794) on UMI microfilm set "Early English books, 1641-1700". Reproductions of the original in the Harvard University Library.
